ActFinancial Administration Act
PrecisOrder amending Schedule I.1 to the Financial Administration Act by striking out the reference to the Minister of State and Leader of the Government in the House of Commons and by substituting for that reference a reference to the Minister of State styled Deputy Leader of the Government in the House of Commons, Minister responsible for Official Languages and Minister responsible for Democratic Reform.
